  "name": "Data Journey Enhancements & More",
  "body": "<p><strong>Release Date</strong> – 2nd March 2021</p>\n<h2 data-id=\"overview\">Overview</h2>\n<p>In this release, you'll find enhancements to the Data Journey feature including the UI redesign. Also noteworthy is the change to the Account Name field in the Account Details page which was changed to a read-only field.</p>\n<p>To learn more about the updates, read on!</p>\n<h2 data-id=\"enhancements\">Enhancements</h2>\n<p><strong>End Date Field in Data Journey</strong></p>\n<p>A new field, End Date, has been introduced in the Data Journey creation flow. This field enables you to specify a date on which the Data Journey will be disabled automatically, saving you the task of remembering to manually disable the Data Journey.</p>\n<p>To learn more about Data Journeys, see <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.maropost.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F360015633773\">Data Journeys</a>.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"New_Data_Journey.png\" height=\"259\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWji.05T5g00000BkWjiEAF.png\" width=\"449\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 259px; width: 449px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWji.05T5g00000BkWjiEAF.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWji.05T5g00000BkWjiEAF.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWji.05T5g00000BkWjiEAF.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWji.05T5g00000BkWjiEAF.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWji.05T5g00000BkWjiEAF.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWji.05T5g00000BkWjiEAF.png 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWji.05T5g00000BkWjiEAF.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>UI Refresh of Data Journey Pages</strong></p>\n<p>The Data Journey pages were redesigned to meet our latest design standards. The UI is now clearer and actions are easier to access; the functionality however remains the same.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Data_Journey_Index_Page.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjj.05T5g00000BkWjjEAF.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjj.05T5g00000BkWjjEAF.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjj.05T5g00000BkWjjEAF.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjj.05T5g00000BkWjjEAF.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjj.05T5g00000BkWjjEAF.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjj.05T5g00000BkWjjEAF.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjj.05T5g00000BkWjjEAF.png 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjj.05T5g00000BkWjjEAF.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Account Name Changed to Read-only Field</strong></p>\n<p>We changed the Account Name field in the Account Details page (Account Details page &gt; ACCOUNT tab) as a read-only field to avoid down-stream backend impacts. You cannot update your account name on the application UI; however, you can reach out to our support team to get it updated.</p>\n<p>To learn about managing your accounts, see <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.maropost.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F360015705613\">Managing Your Accounts</a>.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Account_Details_-_Read-only_Account_Name.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjk.05T5g00000BkWjkEAF.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjk.05T5g00000BkWjkEAF.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjk.05T5g00000BkWjkEAF.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjk.05T5g00000BkWjkEAF.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjk.05T5g00000BkWjkEAF.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjk.05T5g00000BkWjkEAF.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjk.05T5g00000BkWjkEAF.png 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjk.05T5g00000BkWjkEAF.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>",
